svg.text: Evil Teleporter (10) Teleports to Teleporter Exit with matching number, speed and hooks connected to the tee are lost.
Teleporter (26) Teleports to Teleporter Exit with Matching number, resets the teleported tees hook.
Teleporter Exit (27) Exit of various teleporters.
Weapon Teleporter (14) Teleports shots from weapons to Teleporter Exit with matching number.
Hook Teleporter (15) Teleports hooks to Teleporter Exit with matching number.
Checkpoint Teleporter (31) Teleports to Checkpoint Teleporter Exit with the number matching the current checkpoint of the tee, resets the teleported tees hook.
Checkpoint (29) Sets current checkpoint of tee to the displayed number.
Checkpoint Teleporter Exit (30) Teleporter exit for Checkpoint Teleporter.
Evil Checkpoint Teleporter (63) Teleports to Checkpoint Teleporter Exit with the number matching the current checkpoint of the tee, speed and all hooks connected to the tee are lost.
Empty (0) Empty tile, used as an eraser in the map editor.
